steps.name: I click on the more icon represented by three dots for a given item
I should be directed to the Edit Item page
I should be able to view all the item fields
I should be able to edit all the item fields
the application should perform the validations for each respective
I click on the 'Update Item' button
I should see a flash message "Success! Item updated successfully" with a close button to the right
the flash message should disappear within 5 seconds or less
I can close the flash message by clicking on the 'X' button
I should be directed to the Items Page
I should be able to view that the item is updated within the items table
the application database should be updated with the Edits made by me for the respective item
